item.title: Happy New Year!
item.description:
Huge thanks to Tara for helping me get setup for this year's posts!

Thank you all for making 2006 a fun and interesting year. I've never come across such a great group of people as I have on this site. It's been a pleasure to do this. I will try to add some new things in the next few weeks that I hope you will like. I've got a few ideas, it's just a matter of how to do it. I'm learning all of this as I go. Check back on Wednesday for the first show of 2007!

-Angela

posted by Rollins-Archive
